task.summary: Added instructions classes and decoder that turns the ROM bytes into instruction objects.

Added memory module and increased efficiency of Decoder by removing all instruction instantiations and replacing them with reusable instruction instances that are generated when the Decoder is created.
Also added general CPU registers and StatusFlags to represent the state of the flag register.
